people.name: Jean Ann Bowers 1
people.bio: Coached Vevay, Fayetteville and Shawswick High SchoolsA 2-year starter for Bedford High School team leader, as well as class president in 1936 3-year letter winner at Purdue Boiler- makers won 2 Big 10 titles in '38 and '40 captained '40 team as a senior All-American played against Harlem Globetrotters in the Chicago Herald-American's all-star contest, viewed by 22,000 fans in Chicago Stadium played professionally with Firestone before entering service in '41.
